```

2. Open the `Pages\Account\Manage\EnableAuthenticator.cshtml.cs` and search for the following line, inside the `OnGetAsync()` method;

```C#
await LoadSharedKeyAndQrCodeUriAsync(user);
```

Remove the code shown below which follows the call to `LoadSharedKeyAndQrCodeUriAsync(user);`

```C#
